### PR 목록 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pulls
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

###

### PR 목록 - 저장소 필터
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pulls?repoId={{REPO_ID}}
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

###

### PR 목록 - 상태 필터 (OPEN)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pulls?status=OPEN
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

###

### PR 목록 - 페이지네이션
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pulls?page=1&limit=5
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

###

### PR 목록 - 유효하지 않은 status (400 확인)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pulls?status=INVALID
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

###

### Repository 연동 목록 (repoId 확인용)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/repositories
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

###

### [Backfill 테스트] 저장소 연동 → 기존 PR 자동 동기화
# githubId: GitHub 저장소 숫자 ID (github.com/{owner}/{repo} → API로 확인)
# fullName: "owner/repo" 형식
POST http://localhost:3000/api/repositories
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}

{
  "githubId": {{GITHUB_REPO_ID}},
  "name": "{{REPO_NAME}}",
  "fullName": "{{REPO_FULL_NAME}}"
}

###

### [Backfill 확인] 연동 직후 PR 목록 조회 → 데이터 있으면 backfill 성공
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pulls
Cookie: next-auth.session-token={{SESSION_TOKEN}}
